{
  "stem": "3100.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We came in there, and near the acquaintances, we found a little apartment, a room with, with, with a little kitchenette.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we stood there, and from there, we started to go out every day to find out where we could get hooked up to what kind of group to emigrate, to go out, to leave Poland.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, I understand it was the Berihaha called from Palestine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They came young men, and they organized to get out as many Jews from Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we got on that group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told us, on a certain day, about a few weeks later, we have to go out and come to a train, and we will be able-- we will have to walk from a certain place to a station, and then go.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They will-- we will appoint them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One thing, don't have any documents with yourself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't speak Polish, because if you're going to speak Polish, they'll recognize that you're Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You may [INAUDIBLE] in trouble.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what could we do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said, we go as, as a Greek group-- Right.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--And that we go back to Saloniki-- Salonika.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all he should remember is Salonika.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if they approach you and they speak to you, tell them something from the siddur.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, the Polish police went around us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We already are ready to go on the train, to take a ride into-- to border-- cross the border.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They speak.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They speak.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If they come over, they say, [NON-ENGLISH] in Polish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All I told them is [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said something-- another one said [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Another one would say something else in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they got so--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--mixed up, they said, [SPEAKING POLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That means the Greeks are worse than the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
